# alipajand — Project Overview

Personal portfolio for Ali Pajand. Next.js 15 App Router, TypeScript, Tailwind CSS v4, GSAP + Lenis, Resend for email. Deployed to Vercel. No database, no auth.

## Module boundaries

| Module | Responsibility |
|---|---|
| `app/` | Routes, layouts, metadata, API handlers |
| `features/` | Page-level sections (colocated logic) |
| `components/` | Shared, reusable UI |
| `data/` | Static typed content — source of truth for all copy |
| `content/` | Markdown blog posts with gray-matter frontmatter |
| `utils/` | Pure helpers and custom hooks |

## Forbidden without approval

- Public route slugs or URLs (SEO impact)
- `app/api/contact` (live email sending via Resend)
- `.env*` files or environment variables
- Vercel config or deployment targets
- `aria-*` wiring, focus order, or accessibility landmarks
- New npm dependencies with significant bundle cost

## Workflow

```bash
pnpm dev        # dev server
pnpm build      # production build
pnpm test       # Jest
pnpm lint       # ESLint
pnpm typecheck  # tsc
pnpm format     # Prettier
```

Run `pnpm test` before finishing any task.
